flowchart TD
    Q[User request] --> D{Deterministic route?}

    D -->|yes| T[Select registered tool]
    D -->|no| AI[AI planner fallback]

    AI --> T

    T --> E{Tool exists?}
    E -->|no| NO[Say no suitable tool exists]
    E -->|yes| P{Permission level}

    P -->|READ| RUN[Run tool]
    P -->|ACTION| CONF[Ask or verify confirmation]
    P -->|DANGEROUS| CONF

    CONF -->|confirmed| RUN
    CONF -->|not confirmed| STOP[Do not execute]

    RUN --> PHY{Physical command?}
    PHY -->|yes| VER[Verify physical state]
    PHY -->|no| OUT[Return result]

    VER --> OUT[Return cautious result]
